In this equation, ΔP iL = P iL − PiL, Δθfi = θ fi − θfi , and
Δθei = θ ei − θei . If Δθfi = 0 (Δθei = 0), then it is obvious
that state xfi (xei ) is changed (i.e., attacked). Similarly,
we have the following equation that indicates whether a bus
